Class Guest

  • java.lang.Object
    • eventak.Contact
      • eventak.Guest

  • public class Guest
extends Contact
    Guest object. Has everything a Contact has and: - RSVP (attending): default: true/Regrets Only. Guests are attending by default. - address: optional, if an invitation is supposed to be sent by snail mail. - comment: optional, if the guest has any comment
